---
title: HelloHero: Chicken & Lemon Butter Sauce with Zesty Potato Chunks & Herby Mayo
description: Tender pan-seared chicken never fails to satisfy! It has all the familiar tastes of home cooking at its finest, plus a buttery lemon sauce and a side of easy roast potatoes which make up the perfect accompaniments to this tasty dinner.

